to help guide me.

59
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:58,360
Sure.
I’ll help you after I clear of my work.

60
00:04:58,360 --> 00:05:01,600
Great job, Pai.
Send them to me tomorrow.

61
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:04,480
Tomorrow?

62
