75
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:56,560
Can you be responsible for it?

76
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:01,120
I can’t. I’m sorry.

77
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:25,320
Pai, I’m going now.

78
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:27,240
A late night again tonight?

79
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:30,280
It’s just 8 p.m.

80
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:32,680
I’ll wait till it’s a little later.

81
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,920
You’re really strange.

82
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:41,800
No one here
wants to stay late after work.

83
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:46,480
Why?

84
