86
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:58,240
Man, what were you doing?

87
00:06:58,240 --> 00:07:00,000
I’m not joking. It’s true.

88
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:01,760
I’m out. See you tomorrow.

89
00:07:01,760 --> 00:07:02,800
Bye.

90
