So I can finally go home.

92
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:31,440
I’ll go now.

93
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:38,800
Even the ghosts don’t want me here.

94
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:41,320
I’m going now. I’m sorry.

95
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:30,800
