96
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:11,600
Why are you hiding from me?

97
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:16,560
I’m not hiding.

98
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:20,240
I just dropped something.

99
00:09:24,040 --> 00:09:27,360
Are you okay? Why are you acting weird?

100
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:31,160
No. Nothing’s wrong.

101
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:33,800
Nothing at all.

102
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:48,940
I told you already.

103
00:09:48,940 --> 00:09:51,120
I do believe that you’re a real man.

104
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:23,460
