I think Pai has been bit by a zombie.

105
00:10:23,660 --> 00:10:25,280
Just like in the movies.

106
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:28,800
Oh my god, Pai.

107
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:30,920
Why do you look so drained?

108
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:33,800
Would you like one of my vitamins sets?

109
00:10:33,800 --> 00:10:38,520
Or do you want a face moisturizer?

110
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:41,640
Can I change from the vitamins
to something else?

111
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:44,440
Sure. I’ve got everything. Just tell me.

112
00:10:45,560 --> 00:10:48,520
Do you have a new room

113
00:10:48,520 --> 00:10:50,720
with the same price range
as the one I live in now?

114
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:52,600
Oh, why so?

115
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:55,680
Oh, Tookta.

116
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:58,120
The reason I decided to stay

117
00:10:58,120 --> 00:11:01,880
is because I thought
Pupaa didn’t like girls.

118
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:05,360
But now I know the truth.

119
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:09,160
How can you let me live with a guy?

120
00:11:09,160 --> 00:11:13,400
Living with a guy is exciting.

121
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:18,120
