122
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:19,760
What am I going to do?

123
00:11:19,760 --> 00:11:22,920
Well, don’t act like you’re innocent.

124
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:28,840
Alright, I will try
and find one for you.

125
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:31,640
Thank you.

126
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:32,800
Sure.

127
00:11:32,800 --> 00:11:33,760
Bye.

128
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:35,200
Look at yourself.

129
00:11:45,040 --> 00:11:45,800
Block him.

130
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:54,840
Ta, come here.

131
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:00,680
Look at him play.

132
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,400
Go on, Pupaa.

133
00:12:11,720 --> 00:12:15,160
Everyone, let’s take a break.

134
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:17,000
What’s this?

135
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,700
What is going on between you two?

136
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:20,720
You’re off the game.

137
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:25,240
Oh.

138
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:32,280
Hey.

139
00:12:32,680 --> 00:12:33,760
What’s going on? Spill it.

140
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,280
Well,

141
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:40,560
my friend told me

142
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:44,160
there’s a girl who lives with him

143
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:48,160
