147
00:12:57,520 --> 00:12:58,920
A regular guy.

148
00:12:59,520 --> 00:13:00,440
Is he handsome?

149
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:02,480
Well...

150
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:03,320
Well..

151
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:05,160
He looks good.

152
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:09,280
If he looks good,

153
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:10,640
got fair skin,

154
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:12,820
takes care of himself well,

155
00:13:12,900 --> 00:13:14,240
she could misunderstand.

156
00:13:15,280 --> 00:13:19,360
But when she knew he’s a real man,

157
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:21,940
she starts acting strange

158
00:13:21,940 --> 00:13:22,840
when he’s around.

159
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:25,120
What do you think she’s thinking?

160
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:27,160
It’s not that difficult.

161
00:13:27,160 --> 00:13:28,120
She’s just shy, right?

162
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:28,960
She’s afraid.

163
00:13:31,400 --> 00:13:32,200
Afraid?

164
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:33,120
Of course.

165
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:34,560
Well, a guy and a girl,

166
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:37,300
living together in a room.
It’s not weird that she’s afraid of him.

167
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:39,100
Especially if someone like Ta

168
00:13:39,100 --> 00:13:40,760
creeps up on her. She’d be done.

169
00:13:40,760 --> 00:13:41,480
Yeah.

170
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:07,960
Pai, you’re not done yet? So dedicated.

171
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:12,600
Cartoon.

172
00:14:13,160 --> 00:14:15,440
Can I go sleep with you for a few days?

173
00:14:16,880 --> 00:14:18,920
It’s not quite convenient.

174
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:24,320
But I wouldn’t mind for a few days.

175
00:14:24,560 --> 00:14:27,480
Really? Thank you so much.

176
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:28,560
But

177
00:14:29,520 --> 00:14:30,720
