417
00:38:04,640 --> 00:38:05,440
Yeah.

418
00:38:05,720 --> 00:38:07,960
Are you going to pay for me?

419
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:14,280
Hey, what is wrong with you?

420
00:38:15,480 --> 00:38:17,840
