423
00:38:24,600 --> 00:38:27,280
I wasn’t born a genius,

424
00:38:28,280 --> 00:38:30,280
but I wanted to choose this path

425
00:38:30,880 --> 00:38:32,160
and dedicated myself towards it.

426
00:38:32,960 --> 00:38:35,880
When you set a goal,

427
00:38:35,880 --> 00:38:37,040
and dedicate yourself to it,

428
00:38:37,600 --> 00:38:38,600
you’ll be successful.

429
00:38:40,160 --> 00:38:41,600
If you choose to do something,

430
00:38:41,600 --> 00:38:42,560
just do it.

431
00:38:43,080 --> 00:38:44,720
Put in your full effort.

432
00:38:46,040 --> 00:38:47,240
A dedicated person like you,

433
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:50,480
